  I have to admit that prior to becoming Noah’s Dad I had no idea that March 21st was  World Down Syndrome Day . ( So don’t feel bad if you didn’t know either.) 🙂 But it is. And if you will give me about 3 minutes of your time, Noah and I will tell you what it’s all about, and try to give a quick answer to the question, “ What is Down syndrome? ” We put together a short video to tell you a little bit about World Down Syndrome Day and why the date  3:21  is significant. I hope you find it informative and enjoyable! And hey if not, no worries. You’ll still get to see a cute little boy for a few minutes that I’m sure will brighten up your day. So it’s a win either way. 🙂 And if you like videos, be sure to check out  Noah’s Dad on You Tube  where you can watch all of our videos!) // <![CDATA[
